{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":645,"text":"So in college,"},{"time":3349,"text":"I was a government major,"},{"time":4937,"text":"which means I had to write\na lot of papers."},{"time":7423,"text":"Now, when a normal student writes a paper,"},{"time":9495,"text":"they might spread the work out\na little like this."},{"time":11892,"text":"So, you know --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":13067,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":14748,"text":"you get started maybe a little slowly,"},{"time":16599,"text":"but you get enough done in the first week"},{"time":18591,"text":"that, with some heavier days later on,"},{"time":20446,"text":"everything gets done, things stay civil."}]},{"cues":[{"time":22627,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":23853,"text":"And I would want to do that like that."},{"time":26148,"text":"That would be the plan."},{"time":27366,"text":"I would have it all ready to go,"},{"time":29880,"text":"but then, actually, the paper\nwould come along,"},{"time":32398,"text":"and then I would kind of do this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":34363,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":36757,"text":"And that would happen every single paper."}]},{"cues":[{"time":39638,"text":"But then came my 90-page senior thesis,"},{"time":43544,"text":"a paper you're supposed\nto spend a year on."},{"time":45855,"text":"And I knew for a paper like that,\nmy normal work flow was not an option."},{"time":49498,"text":"It was way too big a project."},{"time":50923,"text":"So I planned things out,"},{"time":52100,"text":"and I decided I kind of had\nto go something like this."},{"time":55781,"text":"This is how the year would go."},{"time":57257,"text":"So I'd start off light,"},{"time":59248,"text":"and I'd bump it up in the middle months,"},{"time":61590,"text":"and then at the end,\nI would kick it up into high gear"},{"time":64240,"text":"just like a little staircase."},{"time":65703,"text":"How hard could it be\nto walk up the stairs?"},{"time":68233,"text":"No big deal, right?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":71090,"text":"But then, the funniest thing happened."},{"time":72924,"text":"Those first few months?"},{"time":74791,"text":"They came and went,"},{"time":75982,"text":"and I couldn't quite do stuff."},{"time":77591,"text":"So we had an awesome new revised plan."}]},{"cues":[{"time":79464,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":80655,"text":"And then --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":81838,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":83744,"text":"But then those middle months\nactually went by,"},{"time":86552,"text":"and I didn't really write words,"},{"time":88758,"text":"and so we were here."},{"time":91500,"text":"And then two months turned into one month,"},{"time":94100,"text":"which turned into two weeks."},{"time":95749,"text":"And one day I woke up"},{"time":97724,"text":"with three days until the deadline,"},{"time":101502,"text":"still not having written a word,"},{"time":103457,"text":"and so I did the only thing I could:"},{"time":105540,"text":"I wrote 90 pages over 72 hours,"},{"time":108171,"text":"pulling not one but two all-nighters --"},{"time":110471,"text":"humans are not supposed to pull\ntwo all-nighters --"},{"time":114373,"text":"sprinted across campus,"},{"time":116390,"text":"dove in slow motion,"},{"time":117900,"text":"and got it in just at the deadline."}]},{"cues":[{"time":119980,"text":"I thought that was the end of everything."},{"time":122028,"text":"But a week later I get a call,"},{"time":123611,"text":"and it's the school."},{"time":125757,"text":"And they say, \"Is this Tim Urban?\""},{"time":127420,"text":"And I say, \"Yeah.\""},{"time":128912,"text":"And they say, \"We need\nto talk about your thesis.\""},{"time":131276,"text":"And I say, \"OK.\""},{"time":133468,"text":"And they say,"},{"time":135230,"text":"\"It's the best one we've ever seen.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":137150,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":140014,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":144945,"text":"That did not happen."}]},{"cues":[{"time":146271,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":148433,"text":"It was a very, very bad thesis."}]},{"cues":[{"time":151080,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":153378,"text":"I just wanted to enjoy that one moment\nwhen all of you thought,"},{"time":157502,"text":"\"This guy is amazing!\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":159431,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":160803,"text":"No, no, it was very, very bad."},{"time":163343,"text":"Anyway, today I'm a writer-blogger guy."},{"time":166775,"text":"I write the blog Wait But Why."},{"time":168542,"text":"And a couple of years ago,\nI decided to write about procrastination."},{"time":172302,"text":"My behavior has always perplexed\nthe non-procrastinators around me,"},{"time":175610,"text":"and I wanted to explain\nto the non-procrastinators of the world"},{"time":179322,"text":"what goes on in the heads\nof procrastinators,"},{"time":181453,"text":"and why we are the way we are."},{"time":182917,"text":"Now, I had a hypothesis"},{"time":184097,"text":"that the brains of procrastinators\nwere actually different"},{"time":186976,"text":"than the brains of other people."},{"time":189698,"text":"And to test this, I found an MRI lab"},{"time":191913,"text":"that actually let me scan both my brain"},{"time":194369,"text":"and the brain of a proven\nnon-procrastinator,"},{"time":197048,"text":"so I could compare them."},{"time":198507,"text":"I actually brought them here\nto show you today."},{"time":200732,"text":"I want you to take a look carefully\nto see if you can notice a difference."},{"time":204293,"text":"I know that if you're not\na trained brain expert,"},{"time":206631,"text":"it's not that obvious,\nbut just take a look, OK?"},{"time":208918,"text":"So here's the brain\nof a non-procrastinator."}]},{"cues":[{"time":211835,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":214133,"text":"Now ..."},{"time":216325,"text":"here's my brain."}]},{"cues":[{"time":218280,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":223713,"text":"There is a difference."},{"time":225904,"text":"Both brains have a Rational\nDecision-Maker in them,"},{"time":228316,"text":"but the procrastinator's brain"},{"time":229992,"text":"also has an Instant Gratification Monkey."},{"time":233002,"text":"Now, what does this mean\nfor the procrastinator?"},{"time":235328,"text":"Well, it means everything's fine\nuntil this happens."}]},{"cues":[{"time":237793,"text":"[This is a perfect time\nto get some work done.] [Nope!]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":240439,"text":"So the Rational Decision-Maker\nwill make the rational decision"},{"time":243396,"text":"to do something productive,"},{"time":245316,"text":"but the Monkey doesn't like that plan,"},{"time":247290,"text":"so he actually takes the wheel,"},{"time":248822,"text":"and he says, \"Actually, let's read\nthe entire Wikipedia page"},{"time":251727,"text":"of the Nancy Kerrigan/\nTonya Harding scandal,"},{"time":253887,"text":"because I just remembered\nthat that happened."}]},{"cues":[{"time":256042,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":257082,"text":"Then --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":258264,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":259551,"text":"Then we're going to go over to the fridge,"},{"time":261613,"text":"to see if there's anything new\nin there since 10 minutes ago."},{"time":264503,"text":"After that, we're going to go\non a YouTube spiral"},{"time":267165,"text":"that starts with videos\nof Richard Feynman talking about magnets"},{"time":270439,"text":"and ends much, much later\nwith us watching interviews"},{"time":273179,"text":"with Justin Bieber's mom."}]},{"cues":[{"time":275083,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":277295,"text":"\"All of that's going to take a while,"},{"time":279082,"text":"so we're not going to really have room\non the schedule for any work today."},{"time":282608,"text":"Sorry!\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":283795,"text":"(Sigh)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":286325,"text":"Now, what is going on here?"},{"time":291481,"text":"The Instant Gratification Monkey\ndoes not seem like a guy"},{"time":294196,"text":"you want behind the wheel."},{"time":295474,"text":"He lives entirely in the present moment."},{"time":297443,"text":"He has no memory of the past,\nno knowledge of the future,"},{"time":300295,"text":"and he only cares about two things:"},{"time":302016,"text":"easy and fun."}]},{"cues":[{"time":304338,"text":"Now, in the animal world, that works fine."},{"time":307454,"text":"If you're a dog"},{"time":308686,"text":"and you spend your whole life doing\nnothing other than easy and fun things,"},{"time":312281,"text":"you're a huge success!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":313470,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":315405,"text":"And to the Monkey,"},{"time":317969,"text":"humans are just another animal species."},{"time":320087,"text":"You have to keep well-slept, well-fed\nand propagating into the next generation,"},{"time":324617,"text":"which in tribal times\nmight have worked OK."},{"time":326927,"text":"But, if you haven't noticed,\nnow we're not in tribal times."},{"time":329801,"text":"We're in an advanced civilization,\nand the Monkey does not know what that is."},{"time":333958,"text":"Which is why we have\nanother guy in our brain,"},{"time":336263,"text":"the Rational Decision-Maker,"},{"time":338652,"text":"who gives us the ability to do things\nno other animal can do."},{"time":341703,"text":"We can visualize the future."},{"time":343648,"text":"We can see the big picture."},{"time":345424,"text":"We can make long-term plans."},{"time":346798,"text":"And he wants to take\nall of that into account."},{"time":350138,"text":"And he wants to just have us do"},{"time":351853,"text":"whatever makes sense\nto be doing right now."},{"time":354825,"text":"Now, sometimes it makes sense"},{"time":356238,"text":"to be doing things that are easy and fun,"},{"time":358291,"text":"like when you're having dinner\nor going to bed"},{"time":360466,"text":"or enjoying well-earned leisure time."},{"time":362318,"text":"That's why there's an overlap."},{"time":363792,"text":"Sometimes they agree."},{"time":365560,"text":"But other times, it makes much more sense"},{"time":368406,"text":"to be doing things that are harder\nand less pleasant,"},{"time":372032,"text":"for the sake of the big picture."},{"time":373596,"text":"And that's when we have a conflict."},{"time":376017,"text":"And for the procrastinator,"},{"time":377356,"text":"that conflict tends to end\na certain way every time,"},{"time":379889,"text":"leaving him spending a lot of time\nin this orange zone,"},{"time":383633,"text":"an easy and fun place that's entirely\nout of the Makes Sense circle."},{"time":387984,"text":"I call it the Dark Playground."}]},{"cues":[{"time":390287,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":391935,"text":"Now, the Dark Playground is a place"},{"time":395087,"text":"that all of you procrastinators\nout there know very well."},{"time":398892,"text":"It's where leisure activities happen"},{"time":400720,"text":"at times when leisure activities\nare not supposed to be happening."},{"time":404418,"text":"The fun you have in the Dark Playground"},{"time":406332,"text":"isn't actually fun,\nbecause it's completely unearned,"},{"time":408839,"text":"and the air is filled with guilt,\ndread, anxiety, self-hatred --"},{"time":412078,"text":"all of those good procrastinator feelings."},{"time":414703,"text":"And the question is, in this situation,\nwith the Monkey behind the wheel,"},{"time":418203,"text":"how does the procrastinator ever get\nhimself over here to this blue zone,"},{"time":421820,"text":"a less pleasant place, but where\nreally important things happen?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":425125,"text":"Well, turns out the procrastinator\nhas a guardian angel,"},{"time":430186,"text":"someone who's always looking\ndown on him and watching over him"},{"time":433418,"text":"in his darkest moments --"},{"time":434872,"text":"someone called the Panic Monster."}]},{"cues":[{"time":436991,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":442386,"text":"Now, the Panic Monster\nis dormant most of the time,"},{"time":447270,"text":"but he suddenly wakes up\nanytime a deadline gets too close"},{"time":451196,"text":"or there's danger of public embarrassment,"},{"time":453265,"text":"a career disaster or some other\nscary consequence."},{"time":455800,"text":"And importantly, he's the only thing\nthe Monkey is terrified of."},{"time":459996,"text":"Now, he became very relevant\nin my life pretty recently,"},{"time":464598,"text":"because the people of TED\nreached out to me about six months ago"},{"time":467868,"text":"and invited me to do a TED Talk."}]},{"cues":[{"time":469913,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":475058,"text":"Now, of course, I said yes."},{"time":476989,"text":"It's always been a dream of mine\nto have done a TED Talk in the past."}]},{"cues":[{"time":480818,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":484814,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":492203,"text":"But in the middle of all this excitement,"},{"time":494196,"text":"the Rational Decision-Maker seemed\nto have something else on his mind."},{"time":497521,"text":"He was saying, \"Are we clear\non what we just accepted?"},{"time":500093,"text":"Do we get what's going to be now\nhappening one day in the future?"},{"time":503366,"text":"We need to sit down\nand work on this right now.\""},{"time":505657,"text":"And the Monkey said, \"Totally agree,\nbut let's just open Google Earth"},{"time":508946,"text":"and zoom in to the bottom of India,\nlike 200 feet above the ground,"},{"time":512130,"text":"and scroll up for two and a half hours\ntil we get to the top of the country,"},{"time":515775,"text":"so we can get a better feel for India.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":517777,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":523149,"text":"So that's what we did that day."}]},{"cues":[{"time":524658,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":528604,"text":"As six months turned into four\nand then two and then one,"},{"time":532524,"text":"the people of TED decided\nto release the speakers."},{"time":535643,"text":"And I opened up the website,\nand there was my face"},{"time":538279,"text":"staring right back at me."},{"time":539659,"text":"And guess who woke up?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":541283,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":545430,"text":"So the Panic Monster\nstarts losing his mind,"},{"time":547904,"text":"and a few seconds later,\nthe whole system's in mayhem."}]},{"cues":[{"time":550674,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":555511,"text":"And the Monkey -- remember,\nhe's terrified of the Panic Monster --"},{"time":558636,"text":"boom, he's up the tree!"},{"time":559818,"text":"And finally,"},{"time":560993,"text":"finally, the Rational Decision-Maker\ncan take the wheel"},{"time":563613,"text":"and I can start working on the talk."}]},{"cues":[{"time":565355,"text":"Now, the Panic Monster explains"},{"time":567667,"text":"all kinds of pretty insane\nprocrastinator behavior,"},{"time":571172,"text":"like how someone like me\ncould spend two weeks"},{"time":573530,"text":"unable to start the opening\nsentence of a paper,"},{"time":577398,"text":"and then miraculously find\nthe unbelievable work ethic"},{"time":580193,"text":"to stay up all night\nand write eight pages."},{"time":584385,"text":"And this entire situation,\nwith the three characters --"},{"time":587391,"text":"this is the procrastinator's system."},{"time":590096,"text":"It's not pretty, but in the end, it works."},{"time":593545,"text":"This is what I decided to write about\non the blog a couple of years ago."}]},{"cues":[{"time":597631,"text":"When I did, I was amazed by the response."},{"time":600626,"text":"Literally thousands of emails came in,"},{"time":602803,"text":"from all different kinds of people\nfrom all over the world,"},{"time":605604,"text":"doing all different kinds of things."},{"time":607366,"text":"These are people who were nurses,\nbankers, painters, engineers"},{"time":610356,"text":"and lots and lots of PhD students."}]},{"cues":[{"time":612702,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":614727,"text":"And they were all writing,\nsaying the same thing:"},{"time":617039,"text":"\"I have this problem too.\""},{"time":619015,"text":"But what struck me was the contrast\nbetween the light tone of the post"},{"time":622868,"text":"and the heaviness of these emails."},{"time":624987,"text":"These people were writing\nwith intense frustration"},{"time":628094,"text":"about what procrastination\nhad done to their lives,"},{"time":630880,"text":"about what this Monkey had done to them."},{"time":634902,"text":"And I thought about this, and I said,"},{"time":637892,"text":"well, if the procrastinator's system\nworks, then what's going on?"},{"time":641028,"text":"Why are all of these people\nin such a dark place?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":643538,"text":"Well, it turns out that there's\ntwo kinds of procrastination."},{"time":647987,"text":"Everything I've talked about today,\nthe examples I've given,"},{"time":650845,"text":"they all have deadlines."},{"time":652020,"text":"And when there's deadlines,"},{"time":653342,"text":"the effects of procrastination\nare contained to the short term"},{"time":656291,"text":"because the Panic Monster gets involved."},{"time":658228,"text":"But there's a second kind\nof procrastination"},{"time":660306,"text":"that happens in situations\nwhen there is no deadline."},{"time":662817,"text":"So if you wanted a career\nwhere you're a self-starter --"},{"time":665531,"text":"something in the arts,\nsomething entrepreneurial --"},{"time":667968,"text":"there's no deadlines on those things\nat first, because nothing's happening,"},{"time":671517,"text":"not until you've gone out\nand done the hard work"},{"time":673785,"text":"to get momentum, get things going."},{"time":675435,"text":"There's also all kinds of important things\noutside of your career"},{"time":678537,"text":"that don't involve any deadlines,"},{"time":680166,"text":"like seeing your family or exercising\nand taking care of your health,"},{"time":683455,"text":"working on your relationship"},{"time":684883,"text":"or getting out of a relationship\nthat isn't working."}]},{"cues":[{"time":687588,"text":"Now if the procrastinator's only mechanism\nof doing these hard things"},{"time":692760,"text":"is the Panic Monster, that's a problem,"},{"time":694669,"text":"because in all of these\nnon-deadline situations,"},{"time":697493,"text":"the Panic Monster doesn't show up."},{"time":699145,"text":"He has nothing to wake up for,"},{"time":700621,"text":"so the effects of procrastination,\nthey're not contained;"},{"time":703343,"text":"they just extend outward forever."},{"time":705953,"text":"And it's this long-term\nkind of procrastination"},{"time":708717,"text":"that's much less visible\nand much less talked about"},{"time":711822,"text":"than the funnier, short-term\ndeadline-based kind."},{"time":714747,"text":"It's usually suffered\nquietly and privately."},{"time":718816,"text":"And it can be the source"},{"time":719994,"text":"of a huge amount of long-term\nunhappiness, and regrets."},{"time":724576,"text":"And I thought, that's why\nthose people are emailing,"},{"time":727472,"text":"and that's why they're\nin such a bad place."},{"time":729998,"text":"It's not that they're cramming\nfor some project."},{"time":732766,"text":"It's that long-term procrastination\nhas made them feel like a spectator,"},{"time":736211,"text":"at times, in their own lives."},{"time":738594,"text":"The frustration is not\nthat they couldn't achieve their dreams;"},{"time":741600,"text":"it's that they weren't even\nable to start chasing them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":744713,"text":"So I read these emails\nand I had a little bit of an epiphany --"},{"time":750182,"text":"that I don't think\nnon-procrastinators exist."},{"time":753979,"text":"That's right -- I think all of you\nare procrastinators."},{"time":757898,"text":"Now, you might not all be a mess,"},{"time":759836,"text":"like some of us,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":761210,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":762763,"text":"and some of you may have\na healthy relationship with deadlines,"},{"time":766103,"text":"but remember: the Monkey's sneakiest trick"},{"time":768651,"text":"is when the deadlines aren't there."}]},{"cues":[{"time":771249,"text":"Now, I want to show you one last thing."},{"time":773305,"text":"I call this a Life Calendar."},{"time":776352,"text":"That's one box for every week\nof a 90-year life."},{"time":781345,"text":"That's not that many boxes,"},{"time":782958,"text":"especially since we've already\nused a bunch of those."},{"time":786607,"text":"So I think we need to all take a long,\nhard look at that calendar."},{"time":792977,"text":"We need to think about what\nwe're really procrastinating on,"},{"time":796014,"text":"because everyone is procrastinating\non something in life."},{"time":800782,"text":"We need to stay aware\nof the Instant Gratification Monkey."},{"time":805455,"text":"That's a job for all of us."},{"time":808669,"text":"And because there's not\nthat many boxes on there,"},{"time":810993,"text":"it's a job that should\nprobably start today."}]},{"cues":[{"time":813307,"text":"Well, maybe not today, but ..."}]},{"cues":[{"time":816331,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":817996,"text":"You know."},{"time":819576,"text":"Sometime soon."}]},{"cues":[{"time":821393,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":822626,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}